title: Preview: Tech set for midweek matchup with Tarleton State - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Preview: Tech set for midweek matchup with Tarleton State - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: LUBBOCK, Texas – Coming off an undefeated weekend at home the Red Raiders (12-12) make a trip to Stephenville, Texas for a midweek matchup against Tarleton State (17-6) Wednesday evening.
